Posts.Content: So now my partner has commented to me about my breast looking 'different'. I contacted my doctor to be told to book an appointment for late next week.  Why do I feel like I'm not being taken seriously.
Posts.Title: Don't know what to do

Posts.Content: Thank you.  I've rang back and will need to speak to a female doctor after 2pm. Fingers crossed they actually call. I know there's something not right. If it turns out to be nothing then at least I know but if it is, I'd rather not wait around.
